# Preserve console.log

Do not delete, comment out, or replace existing `console.log` calls while making other changes.

Only remove or clean up `console.log` when the user explicitly asks (e.g. "remove console.logs", "clean up debug logs").

When adding new code, avoid introducing unnecessary `console.log` unless useful for the task — but leave existing ones intact.
